[src:analytic-number-theory/dirichlet-series] The non-zero multiplicative functions form a subgroup of the group of units of Ω.
[src:analytic-number-theory/dirichlet-series] The ring of formal Dirichlet series over **C** is isomorphic to a ring of formal power series in countably many variables.
